Cases.

Workflow.

I divide work into stages with approval at each step.
Design

Creating project design.
My favorite part.
Creating graphic elements, selecting content, fonts and color palette

Launch Preparation

Connecting domain

Setting up SSL certificate

SEO optimization

Connecting metrics and analytics

Development & Responsive

Responsive design adaptation for all screens and mobile devices.
Remember that mobile traffic now accounts for about 80% of all users

Prototyping

I create a prototype / skeleton of the future site with complete text content and layout.
This stage determines the sequence of site blocks and properly structures the customer journey

Analytics

Serious preparation stage for website creation.
I research your competitors, evaluate and highlight important details. I find strengths and weaknesses and use them in website creation

Contract Signing

Drafting and signing the contract by all parties

Briefing

We meet and get acquainted.
Discussing project goals and objectives.
I fully immerse myself in business processes and generate the best ideas
